do n't waste your money this is a good book for those who know how to use a pda and are experts at reading and writing code . it is not for beginners or those who have never seen win ce . but if you love computers and techie gadgets , are good with code and like to play with electronic toys , are looking for another techie 's love of toys , then you might get something out of it . but if you are inclined in that way you already know this stuff . do n't waste your money . there are other books that do a better job in both area